race.description: Christmas Party Nights At Dundalk Stadium Apprentice Handicap
race.comment: TRISHULI RIVER (5) holds solid course form after going down by 1L over 2414m at this track. Looks in great order and expected to deliver a bold showing. SINBAD MY DAD (1) brings a modest strike-rate. Ran well last time tackling 2112m at this track finishing just 1L from the winner. Consider. OZARK DAZE (4) is a twenty one start maiden who finished fourth last time attempting 2112m here. Finds a suitable race though could prove vulnerable from a win perspective. GREY FABLE (13) missed the frame past two starts. Holds ability judging by recent efforts after finishing fifth 4.5L behind in a 2414m contest here. Claims.
